productText.text:
An easy way to get your veggies every day! Each 8 oz. glass contains 2 servings of veggies*  
 
 

*8 fl. oz. juice provides 2 servings (1/2 cup each) of vegetables. The 2010 Dietary Guidelines for Americans recommend 2 1/2 cups of a variety of vegetables per day for a 2,000 calorie diet.
